OL,3,CAttempted murder arrest after man
OL,4,Cseriously injured in Bristol shooting
OL,6,FThree people have been arrested after
OL,7,Fa man in a car was shot in broad
OL,8,Fdaylight in Bristol on Wednesday, 1
OL,9,FApril.
OL,11,FAn investigation was launched after a
OL,12,Fshot was fired at a car on Speedwell
OL,13,FRoad at around 1.45pm. The victim, in
OL,14,Fhis 20s, remains in hospital with
OL,15,Fserious injuries.
OL,1,W~s1j5 hw1~k4~c1 hw}h7}j7}      G1/4
