OL,0,        ECIMSBWebfax 1   F431A1775106076
OL,3,CAttempted murder arrest after man
OL,4,Cseriously injured in Bristol shooting
OL,6,FA man in his twenties was arrested on
OL,7,Fsuspicion of attempted murder, just
OL,8,Fafter 2.30am on Thursday, 2 April.
OL,9,FAnother man and woman in their
OL,10,Ftwenties have been arrested on
OL,11,Fsuspicion of assisting an offender.
OL,13,FPolice say the victim's injuries are
OL,14,F"potentially life-changing".
OL,1,W~s1j5 hw1~k4~c1 hw}h7}j7}      G2/4
OL,2,W,.!+.-' "-$/*%+.!+,*%/*%/*-'T(,,,,,,,,,
