FL,432,430,120,260,000,100
PN,43103
SC,0003
CT,2,C
PS,c008
OL,0,        ECIMSBWebfax 1   F431A1775106076
OL,3,CAttempted murder arrest after man
OL,4,Cseriously injured in Bristol shooting
OL,6,FAvon and Somerset Police say they're
OL,7,Fnot looking for anyone else in
OL,8,Fconnection with this incident, but a
OL,9,Fheightened police presence and a scene
OL,10,Fwill remain at St Anne's Woods, near
OL,11,FBrislington, as an area of interest
OL,12,Fand also the Speedwell area of Bristol.
OL,14,FThe force added: "We understand that
OL,15,Fthis may have been a very concerning
OL,16,Fincident, but we have deployed a
OL,17,Fsignificant number of resources as
OL,18,Fpart of our response, including the
OL,19,FNational Police Air Service
OL,20,Fhelicopter, specially-trained firearms
OL,21,Fofficers and drone units.
OL,1,W~s1j5 hw1~k4~c1 hw}h7}j7}      G3/4
OL,2,W,.!+.-' "-$/*%+.!+,*%/*%/*-'T(,,,,,,,,,
