OL,24,ANext Page BSW Eng NewsCThis Day FReg TV
FL,432,430,120,260,000,100
PN,43104
SC,0004
CT,2,C
PS,c008
OL,0,        ECIMSBWebfax 1   F431A1775106076
OL,3,CAttempted murder arrest after man
OL,4,Cseriously injured in Bristol shooting
OL,6,F"We continue to appeal for anyone who
OL,7,Fwitnessed the incident to come
OL,8,Fforward, including anyone with footage
OL,9,Fof the incident. If you can help,
OL,10,Fplease call us."
OL,12,FAt the time of the incident nearby
OL,13,Froads were sealed off and a number of
OL,14,Flocal schools, including Two Mile Hill
OL,15,FSchool and Bristol Brunel Academy,
OL,16,Fwere put in lockdown for a time to
OL,17,Fensure the safety of children.
OL,19,FThe cordon around Speedwell Road was
OL,20,Ffully lifted shortly after 8pm on 1
OL,21,FApril.
OL,1,W~s1j5 hw1~k4~c1 hw}h7}j7}      G4/4
